languages.text: "Касс, ты... несправедлива ко мне. Представь, за то время, что мы провели рядом, я к тебе прикипела. И... ну... мне жаль, девочка. Мне правда жаль".
"Cass, you're... you're not being fair to me. Funnily enough, after all the time we've spent together, I've grown fond of you. And... well... I'm sorry, Cass. I really am."

languages.text: “小卡，你……你对我太不公平了。真有意思，我们在相处了这么长一段时间后，我已经开始喜欢上你了。可是……嗯……我很抱歉，小卡，我真的很抱歉。”
languages.original_text: "Cass, you're... you're not being fair to me. Funnily enough, after all the time we've spent together, I've grown fond of you. And... well... I'm sorry, Cass. I really am."

languages.text: « Cass, vous... vous êtes injuste avec moi. Croyez-le ou non, mais depuis tout ce temps, je m'étais attachée à vous. Et... euh... Je suis désolée, Cass. Vraiment. »

languages.text: «Cass, no... no estás siendo justa conmigo. Irónicamente, después de todo el tiempo que hemos pasado juntas, te he cogido cariño. Y... bueno... Lo siento, Cass. De verdad».

languages.text: 「カシア、あなた…フェアじゃないわ。妙なことに、一緒に過ごしているうちに、あなたのことが好きになってしまったんたんだけどね。そして…その…ごめんなさい、カシア。本当に。」
languages.original_text: "Cass, you're... you're not being fair to me. Funnily enough, after all the time we've spent together, I've grown fond of you. And... well... I'm sorry, Cass. I really am."

languages.text: "Cass, Ihr ... Ihr seid nicht fair zu mir. Lustigerweise habe ich Euch nach der langen gemeinsamen Zeit liebgewonnen. Und ... nun ja ... Es tut mir leid, Cass. Wirklich."

languages.text: "Cass, bana haksızlık ediyorsun. Tuhaftır... Geçirdiğimiz bunca zamanda sana kanım ısındı. Diyeceğim şu ki... Üzgünüm Cass. Çok üzgünüm."
